<i>Things got a little... heated.</i>

510
00:29:36,156 --> 00:29:38,491
<i>But I'm here</i>
<i>in Pine Grove now.</i>

511
00:29:38,619 --> 00:29:40,124
Yeah? What brings you here?

512
00:29:40,252 --> 00:29:41,723
<i>You, Sidney.</i>

513
00:29:41,851 --> 00:29:45,499
<i>You were missed in New York.</i>
<i>It's not the same without you.</i>

514
00:29:45,627 --> 00:29:47,995
<i>I guess you couldn't</i>
<i>be bothered now that you're</i>

515
00:29:48,122 --> 00:29:50,939
<i>so busy with a husband</i>
<i>and family.</i>

516
00:29:51,067 --> 00:29:52,604
Well, you sure know
a lot about me

517
00:29:52,732 --> 00:29:54,107
for another asshole
hiding behind

518
00:29:54,235 --> 00:29:55,675
a fake number
and a voice changer.

519
00:29:55,802 --> 00:29:59,899
<i>Oh, I'm not hiding,</i>
<i>Sidney. Not this time.</i>

520
00:30:08,155 --> 00:30:10,331
<i>Surprise, Sidney.</i>

521
00:30:12,187 --> 00:30:13,628
<i>Do you need a minute? Oh!</i>
<i>Oh, my gosh.</i>

522
00:30:13,756 --> 00:30:15,676
<i>It looks like you need</i>
<i>a minute. I'll wait.</i>

523
00:30:17,564 --> 00:30:19,291
Nice try. Stu Macher is dead.

524
00:30:19,420 --> 00:30:22,843
<i>Oh, gosh.</i>
<i>I'm gonna agree to</i>
<i>disagree with you there.</i>

525
00:30:24,092 --> 00:30:26,555
<i>Oh, my God!</i>
<i>It is so good to see you.</i>

526
00:30:26,683 --> 00:30:29,212
<i>I always had</i>
<i>a thing for you, Sid!</i>

527
00:30:30,427 --> 00:30:32,315
<i>It's gonna be so much fun.</i>

528
00:30:32,443 --> 00:30:36,379
<i>Just like the old days,</i>
<i>except now there's no Billy</i>
<i>or Randy or Tatum.</i>

529
00:30:36,507 --> 00:30:38,139
<i>Speaking of whom,</i>
<i>your daughter,</i>

530
00:30:38,267 --> 00:30:40,859
<i>her name's Tatum.</i>
<i>That is so adorable.</i>

531
00:30:40,987 --> 00:30:45,659
<i>I mean, It's a little weird or</i>
<i>whatever, but it's supercute.</i>

532
00:30:45,787 --> 00:30:47,867
<i>And she is</i>

533
00:30:49,052 --> 00:30:50,651
<i>so pretty.</i>

534
00:30:50,779 --> 00:30:52,892
Do not talk about my daughter.

535
00:30:53,020 --> 00:30:54,331
<i>Oh. Okay, yeah.</i>

536
00:30:54,459 --> 00:30:56,092
<i>I should definitely</i>
<i>tell you, though,</i>

537
00:30:56,219 --> 00:30:59,291
<i>I am currently outside of</i>
<i>her high school theater.</i>

538
00:30:59,932 --> 00:31:01,947
Don't you fucking dare!

539
00:31:02,075 --> 00:31:03,708
<i>It's showtime, bitch.</i>

540
00:31:06,396 --> 00:31:07,835
Hey, Chief.

541
00:31:08,762 --> 00:31:10,075
You're gonna want to
hear this.

542
00:31:10,204 --> 00:31:11,963
I just got a call from
the police in Woodsboro.

543
00:31:12,092 --> 00:31:13,947
Just a sec.

544
00:31:14,076 --> 00:31:14,972
Hey, babe.

545
00:31:16,315 --> 00:31:17,499
You need to go to the theater
right now.

546
00:31:17,627 --> 00:31:18,940
<i>What? What--</i>

547
00:31:19,068 --> 00:31:20,764
There's a killer, Mark.
He's going for Tatum.

548
00:31:20,891 --> 00:31:23,323
I'm on it. All available units
to the high school theater now!

549
00:31:23,451 --> 00:31:25,532
<i>I'm on my way, babe.</i>
Mark, hurry.

550
00:31:53,308 --> 00:31:56,059
Start with liftoffs
and landings, okay?

551
00:31:56,188 --> 00:31:57,180
Got it.

552
00:31:59,611 --> 00:32:00,699
Ready?

553
00:32:00,827 --> 00:32:01,916
Ready.

554
00:32:05,499 --> 00:32:07,836
Okay, a little hard
on the landing there.

555
00:32:07,964 --> 00:32:09,211
Sorry.

556
00:32:11,035 --> 00:32:12,860
It's just too jerky.

557
00:32:12,987 --> 00:32:14,651
Softer.
Got it.

558
00:32:17,019 --> 00:32:19,003
Huh?

559
00:32:19,131 --> 00:32:20,731
Try it again.

560
00:32:22,939 --> 00:32:24,956
Okay, any day now!
Oh.

561
