<i>Relax.</i>
<i>I'm not going to hurt her</i>

1404
01:27:46,783 --> 01:27:48,894
<i>until you're here</i>
<i>to see it.</i>

1405
01:27:49,023 --> 01:27:51,711
Where are you?
<i>Where the heart is...</i>

1406
01:27:51,838 --> 01:27:54,527
