my abusive marriage, right?

1494
01:33:16,255 --> 01:33:18,495
I was really trapped,
and I couldn't see a way out.

1495
01:33:18,622 --> 01:33:22,944
But then I read
<i>Out of Darkness</i>
by Sidney Prescott.

1496
01:33:23,070 --> 01:33:24,704
Oh, it's such a great book!

1497
01:33:24,832 --> 01:33:29,279
And then I realized that
your life, it comes down to
one simple truth.

1498
