Sidney Prescott kills
the bad guy.

1499
01:33:34,783 --> 01:33:36,224
That's your purpose.

1500
01:33:37,087 --> 01:33:40,383
You are a real-life
scream queen.

1501
01:33:41,024 --> 01:33:42,591
The final girl.

1502
01:33:43,839 --> 01:33:45,792
God, you inspire me!

1503
01:33:46,815 --> 01:33:50,463
So I started planning
and doing Pilates,

1504
01:33:50,592 --> 01:33:53,343
and then I pulled a Sidney

1505
