I wanted people to see
there was life after trauma.

1514
01:34:13,983 --> 01:34:15,488
But there isn't for you!

1515
01:34:16,735 --> 01:34:19,710
Trauma is your life.

1516
01:34:20,480 --> 01:34:21,504
When you disappeared,

1517
01:34:21,630 --> 01:34:23,583
do you know how much
that hurt me?

1518
01:34:23,711 --> 01:34:26,272
I mean,
I couldn't fucking handle it!

1519
01:34:26,399 --> 01:34:27,807
I checked myself
into a facility.

1520
01:34:27,936 --> 01:34:29,503
Fallbrook.
That's where we met.

1521
01:34:29,631 --> 01:34:32,000
Okay, I'm talking,
so don't interrupt me, okay?

1522
01:34:32,128 --> 01:34:34,175
Great. Fuck.
Where the fuck was I?

1523
01:34:34,303 --> 01:34:35,968
Shit. Fuck!

1524
