New York. Pilates.
You disappeared.

1525
01:34:38,367 --> 01:34:40,479
Fallbrook.
Fallbrook. Fallbrook, yes!

1526
01:34:40,608 --> 01:34:43,102
It was the closest psychiatric
center that I could find

1527
01:34:43,231 --> 01:34:45,951
because I had to be near you.

1528
01:34:47,264 --> 01:34:51,968
And that finally brings us
to tonight.

1529
01:34:52,095 --> 01:34:54,719
Okay, Jessica, you're right,
I've been selfish.

1530
01:34:54,848 --> 01:34:57,024
I can do better.
We can start over.

1531
01:34:57,150 --> 01:34:58,815
I am starting over.

1532
