You got to shoot her
in the head.

1568
01:38:23,040 --> 01:38:24,799
What?
Shoot her in the--

1569
01:38:25,952 --> 01:38:26,783
Shit!

1570
01:38:26,912 --> 01:38:28,959
Damn it. Okay.

1571
01:38:33,536 --> 01:38:34,784
Come on.

1572
01:38:58,206 --> 01:38:59,488
You okay?

1573
01:39:03,039 --> 01:39:05,472
I'm Sidney
fucking Prescott's daughter.

1574
01:39:13,470 --> 01:39:14,943
Past my prime.

1575
01:39:16,255 --> 01:39:17,406
Fuck you.

1576
01:39:26,910 --> 01:39:29,343
This is Robbie Rivers
with an exclusive

1577
