And fierce.

1608
01:41:52,096 --> 01:41:55,455
She wasn't afraid of anything.

1609
01:41:58,943 --> 01:42:01,823
So that's why
I named you Tatum.

1610
01:42:02,592 --> 01:42:05,696
Because that was my wish

1611
01:42:06,270 --> 01:42:07,456
